Acknowledgements

APIs mirror the BSD queue/tree interfaces while replacing raw pointers with indices to enable robust shared-memory deployments.
The cuckoo hash table follows the XOR-based two-bucket scheme for O(1) amortised insert with prefetch-driven staged lookup.